<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" android:versionCode="1" android:versionName="1.0.0" package="jp.joao.preferenceseditor.sample" platformBuildVersionCode="23" platformBuildVersionName="6.0-2704002">
	<uses-sdk android:minSdkVersion="4" android:targetSdkVersion="23" />
	<application android:label="Preferences Editor" android:name="jp.joao.preferenceseditor.sample.DebugApplication" android:debuggable="true">
		<activity android:name="jp.joao.preferenceseditor.sample.MainActivity">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
			</intent-filter>
		</activity>
		<receiver android:name="jp.joao.preferenceseditor.PreferencesEditorReceiver" android:exported="true">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="jp.joao.preferenceseditor.sample.sp.PUT" />
				<action android:name="jp.joao.preferenceseditor.sample.sp.REMOVE" />
				<action android:name="jp.joao.preferenceseditor.sample.sp.CLEAR" />
			</intent-filter>
		</receiver>
		<activity android:theme="@android:style/Theme.Translucent.NoTitleBar" android:name="com.jakewharton.processphoenix.ProcessPhoenix" android:process=":phoenix" />
	</application>
</manifest>
